My 30 year reunion @ St.Bernadette was so special! 
I went to school with Most of my classmates from kindergarden through 8th grade and haven’t seen many of them since the last day we walked out of this school in 8th grade! When I seen them we picked up right where we left off … that feeling alone was pretty Amazing!
The memories we make in our life will last a lifetime! That’s why We have to keep on making them!!!! 
Thank you Sister Jospehine you have touched our life’s in ways you can’t imagine! 
It was a honor to make Sister Jo smile and make her feel good because she really deserved it! 
Salute to everyone who came out and made this day very special! 🙏❤️
#Sisterjosephine #St.Bernadette #Reunion #blessed #thankful #cuzolove❤️
